review_blob: Nice big DIPA without an overpowering bitterness.. Nice malty backbone makes this 100 IBU beer very drinkable. Pours a dark golden color, nice lacing in the glass. Will be looking for this one in the stores. Sold in bombers only
beer_name: Figure Eight Snake Pro Double IPA

review_blob: Great drinkable beer! Hoppy note yet not overpowering. Refreshing finish, too easy to drink. Cant wait to have another!
